name: CaashCow
description: Since Caash.io launched, we’ve made tons of progress. Our beautiful dex, unique referral system, staking platform and community have grown tremendously. We’re excited to introduce a sibling to CASH token, CaashCow (COW). Its purpose is to be the reward token for staking CASH and its tokenomics directly benefit CASH (see https://docs.caash.io/cow).
